  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000016",
    "sentence": "初，后嘗於室內，忽見庭前昌蒲生花，光彩照灼，非世中所有。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000017",
    "sentence": "后驚視，謂侍者曰：「汝見不？」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000018",
    "sentence": "對曰：「不見。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000019",
    "sentence": "后曰：「嘗聞見者當富貴。」",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000020",
    "sentence": "因遽取吞之。",
    "entities": []
  },
  {
    "sentence_id": "HCH_011_007_000021",
    "sentence": "是月產高祖。",
